column1: # Definition: Antiretroviral therapy coverage indicates the percentage of adults and children with advanced HIV infection currently receiving antiretroviral therapy among the estimated number of people needing antiretroviral therapy based on WHO 2010 guidelines.
# Source: UN Inter-Agency and Expert Group on Gender Statistics (IAEG-GS)
